# Notarization credentials for `bun run package:notarize` / `package:publish`.
# Copy to .env.local (gitignored) and fill in — the scripts source it before
# invoking electron-builder. Values are personal/secret; never commit the
# real file.
#
# Code SIGNING needs no env at all: electron-builder auto-discovers the
# Developer ID Application certificate from the keychain (a machine without
# the cert builds unsigned with a warning instead of failing).
#
# App Store Connect API key (Users and Access > Integrations) — the
# CI-friendly path, no Apple-ID password / 2FA dance. electron-builder picks
# these three up automatically; their presence is also what flips the
# `notarize` gate in electron-builder.cjs.
APPLE_API_KEY="/path/to/AuthKey_XXXXXXXXXX.p8"
APPLE_API_KEY_ID="XXXXXXXXXX"
APPLE_API_ISSUER="xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx"
